{"tid":470124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"校園直播李飛演講　老師派發工作紙　有學生掩臉休息","createTime":"2017-11-16T04:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T12:02:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"094ab9bb4f31a0bf6604415fffbfa4271f1de244","tid":470124,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171116/s00001/9c6defe2d415bb88151cda60766338e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171116%2Fs00001%2F9c6defe2d415bb88151cda60766338e9.jpg&h=e2777211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171116/s00001/9c6ea7f3a290457c76400a213da73274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171116%2Fs00001%2F9c6ea7f3a290457c76400a213da73274.jpg&h=b2233980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171116/s00001/9c6fae9691a1c731adcd2639f119a0ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171116%2Fs00001%2F9c6fae9691a1c731adcd2639f119a0ca.jpg&h=71ace357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會基本法委員會主任李飛今早出席基本法研討會演講。獅子會中學今天安排學生看直播，直播前由老師向學生講解什麼是基本法和憲法；校方亦設李飛講話工作紙給學生填寫。<br />\n<br />\n李飛的演講主題是「國家憲法和基本法下，香港作為特區的角色及使命」，約演說50分鐘。開始數分鐘後，有學生填寫工作紙，亦有學生掩臉休息。<br />\n<br />\n獅子會中學安排了中三、中五和中六約100名學生觀看直播，校方在研討會開始前半小時安排學生進入禮堂，並由老師向學生簡介憲法和基本法，如憲法由來、基本法由來等，以及提醒學生留意不同傳媒報道研討會的手法。<br />\n<br />\n校方亦向學生派發工作紙問卷，要求學生根據李飛講話，回答什麼是憲法、基本法的法律地位、基本法對落實一國兩制的意義和基本作對本港繁榮所起的作用等。問卷則問及學生對直播內容和安排的看法，如課堂對學習的幫助、講解內容是否清晰及容易明白、演講是否對學生有得益等，叫學生給分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171116/s00001/1510801713805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171116%2Fs00001%2F1510801713805&d=f5FGq3ggdxP5DuSvVviHgZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d40f2a4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171116%2Fs00001%2F1510801713805&h=69c5ebba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171116/s00001/1510801713805</a>"},{"pid":"7447f6e9d4cfd05cf8ad36f1ec9a4043cc30bf18","tid":470124,"uid":133529,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"我係班中六,寧願上堂操PAST PAPER啦屌"},{"pid":"46722e6f42a4160a2424b180d745880c8548ad88","tid":470124,"uid":9069,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:49:57.000Z","msg":"正 有得訓"},{"pid":"cda2377576286c3c9cccfa129ec6c0a4cd42cf18","tid":470124,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c63e14a594359a585b1c2a0d32dcf929cca16b9","tid":470124,"uid":41508,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:53:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d11e111a8f228b5906e2210d0d05d3990b326749","tid":470124,"uid":11578,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"夠膽就企起身反鳩班仆街"},{"pid":"e2128192f990060ba5bd1ff06cf315cf3810a1ad","tid":470124,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a89217a60ef0b7871a149db756f7dcab3a5c81","tid":470124,"uid":27411,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"白痴仔先真係會理呢啲廢話<br />\n有腦既都知佢講既野唔係法律<br />\n白紙黑字寫既先係法律既依據<br />\n我理得佢講一國一制 一國三制 一國十制都好<br />\n都係唔會成為到法律既依據 亦都唔會係事實"},{"pid":"6329e825824fbedddc12c228028ba5bd1647b630","tid":470124,"uid":1886,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171116/s00001/9c6ea7f3a290457c76400a213da73274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171116%2F